{"tid":155314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終審法院一致裁定陳志雲叢培崑上訴得直　撤銷兩人定罪","createTime":"2017-03-14T02:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T06:43:43.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47bc111c749cd423671184737c32662d24d88e57","tid":155314,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:18:40.000Z","msg":"無綫電視前業務總經理陳志雲就串謀代理人收受利益案，上訴至終審法院。終院今日頒下終極裁決，判陳志雲及另一名被告叢培崑上訴得直，撤銷兩人定罪。<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲被控2009年擔任無綫電視業務總經理時，因在未經無綫同意下，收取11萬2千元酬金，在律政司去年底第二度上訴得直後，被判罰款8萬4千元，叢培崑被罰2萬8千元。"},{"pid":"3e3beac2c178696d674bf79a007e4c8d8ee745c5","tid":155314,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:21:24.000Z","msg":"唔洗做首席智囊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1818bfc680cfee53bfa384b6d785b3c138592eb6","tid":155314,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9a3991b366d243cee7513caebdd50f79216739d","tid":155314,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比你打贏又點<br />\n都比人鬥左落黎</blockquote><br />\n唔洗入去受喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8a04467fc7ca37b746d636005d7ef8eaa22cfd","tid":155314,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比你打贏又點<br />\n都比人鬥左落黎</blockquote><br />\n唔洗入去受喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢本來都係判罰錢姐"},{"pid":"96834266b6534c871e150abd1140d454c5af787e","tid":155314,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"打咗幾多錢官司？<br />\n<br />\n一般人有無本事可以打到去終審？"},{"pid":"c57526d2c28e67e398931cf77d22c7210ef12116","tid":155314,"uid":7486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打咗幾多錢官司？<br />\n<br />\n一般人有無本事可以打到去終審？<